<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="size-n">size <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /saɪz/    美 /saɪz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>大小；规模：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Jim’s a small boy of my own size.
吉米是个小男孩，个子和我差不多。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Built from lightweight materials, the robots are about <strong>the size of</strong> a human arm or smaller.
这些机器人由轻型材料制成，和人的胳膊差不多大或者更小一些。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>尺码：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What size do you want / take? 
你穿多大尺码的？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They didn’t have the trousers <strong>in my size</strong>.
那款裤子没有我的尺码。</p></div></div>